# Implementation Plan - Project AssetFlow (Stage 3)

Transition the system from mock data to a fully integrated E2E application with a proactive notification engine for Microsoft Teams.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - We will install **Recharts** for frontend visualization.
> - We will install **APScheduler** and **HTTPX** for the backend notification engine.
> - The backend will require a valid `TEAMS_WEBHOOK_URL` in `config.py` for notifications to work (we will use a placeholder for now).

